74
00:08:48,190 --> 00:08:52,490
This Devil General has become a target of public criticism.

75
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:55,110
He'd better not implicate the rest of us!

76
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:59,120
That's right. From what I see, Royal Father, you should sever all ties with them as soon as possible.

77
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,730
You should chase Shen Jin out of this home.

78
00:09:00,730 --> 00:09:05,180
Being married to a criminal official is such a disgrace to the family.

79
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:10,430
When will Princess Consort and Consort Xu return to the manor?

80
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:14,400
Princess Consort and Consort Xu are at the palace keeping Empress Dowager company.

81
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,980
I'm afraid it will be a few days before they are back.

82
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:40,690
Why are you here again? The general is no longer here at the manor.

83
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:42,610
I...

84
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:47,450
I was afraid... you'd be sad because Her Ladyship has left.

85
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:52,370
You are quite attentive.

86
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:59,530
When it comes to things that pertain to Miss Xiao Cong... I take them to heart.

87
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:03,560
Thank you.

88
