89
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:10,510
Who did you say likes you?

90
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,900
You like me!

91
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:14,670
- I... <br> - You gifted me clothes and chatted with me.

92
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:17,700
You also always like to look at me.

93
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:19,810
Stop spouting nonsense!

94
00:10:19,810 --> 00:10:23,540
Hurry up and leave. Stop coming to the general's manor.

95
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:29,140
Miss Xiao Cong, you really have a straightforward personality. Such a heroic spirit!

96
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:33,620
Miss Xiao Cong!

97
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:37,540
She's even capable of being shy. That makes me like her even more.

98
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:43,800
Rou Rou! It's the steamed buns you like.

99
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,500
Miss, should we go and eat it later?

100
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,080
Sure!

101
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:50,420
- There is great entertainment! <br> - There are lots of good food, too!

102
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:54,690
We must take a nice walk around here another day.

103
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:57,730
It's so beautiful. I feel as if everything's changed.

104
00:10:57,730 --> 00:11:00,410
<i>That's right, I don't recognize anything anymore.</i>

105
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:02,190
<i>Look over there!</i> <br>- Stop.

106
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:15,220
Jin'er, go on ahead to the Rui Royal Manor first.

107
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:17,750
Husband, aren't you coming with me?

108
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:21,350
I must report to the imperial court. It cannot be delayed.

109
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:24,520
Jin'er, remember,

110
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:29,490
endure everything for the time being at the Rui Royal Manor before I return.

111
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:31,780
We will talk once I return.

112
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,720
I understand.

113
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:42,330
Husband, be careful!

114
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:46,340
Miss, I want to go with the general as well.

115
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:48,720
That way, I'd be able to see Su Su.

116
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:53,220
It'll be fine. You'll get to see your Su Su once the general returns.

117
00:12:07,490 --> 00:12:10,890
<i>[Rui Royal Manor]</i>

118
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,820
Miss, be careful.

119
00:12:14,990 --> 00:12:16,270
Mother.

120
00:12:16,270 --> 00:12:18,450
I'm back.

121
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:22,070
Miss, say, if they find out about the general's situation,

122
00:12:22,070 --> 00:12:24,630
will they bully us?

123
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:28,380
Since we are here, we shall make the best of things.

124
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:32,400
No matter what, we must endure until the general comes back.

125
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:35,460
Then let's quickly go inside.

126
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:38,830
<i>[Rui Royal Manor]</i>

127
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:45,140
<i>We are all Lord Yongning's former subordinates.</i>

128
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:48,090
<i> Seeing His Majesty's posture, it seems that the general is going to be convicted. </i>

129
00:12:48,090 --> 00:12:51,660
<i> Why has His Majesty transferred us back to the capital? </i>

130
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:56,090
It's to set an example for us military officers. He is "killing the chicken to warn the monkey."

131
00:12:56,090 --> 00:12:58,900
He is warning us to not follow in the general's footsteps.

132
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:03,180
For many years, the general has fought on the battlefield for this nation and its people.

133
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:05,670
How can His Majesty treat him like this?

134
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:10,960
<i> Summoning Lord Yongning, Chu Xiuming, into the hall! </i>

135
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:24,030
I, Chu Xiuming, have come to pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

136
00:13:25,930 --> 00:13:30,030
Lord Yongning, you are back.

137
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:33,250
I have guarded the borders for many years and have fulfilled my duties faithfully.

138
00:13:33,250 --> 00:13:35,920
This time, in accordance with the decree, I have returned to the imperial court to see Your Majesty.

139
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,480
I did not dare dismiss the order.

140
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:40,300
What a great phrase, "fulfilling one's duties faithfully."

141
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:42,990
Chu Xiuming, do you know what you've committed?!

142
00:13:42,990 --> 00:13:45,900
I don't know what crime I have committed.

143
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:50,160
Minister Liu, tell us.

144
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:53,260
Yes, Your Majesty.

145
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,780
Quickly. Move everything quickly.

146
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:59,220
She won't have this imperial honorary title much longer.

147
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:03,050
If she wants to blame someone, then she should blame her disappointing daughter.

148
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:06,350
She is convicted of crimes, what an inauspicious daughter!

149
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:08,200
What are you doing?!

150
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:12,210
Speaking of the devil.

151
00:14:12,210 --> 00:14:14,930
Guards! Capture this degenerate of our family.

152
00:14:14,930 --> 00:14:18,190
Who dares to lay a hand on her? She's the general's lady.

153
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:24,620
Elder Sister Zi. Fourth Young Sister. Long time no see.

154
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:27,570
I came to see my mother. Could you let me through?

155
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,750
The general's lady?

156
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:33,500
How amusing.

157
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,290
The whole capital knows

158
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:39,630
that your husband, Chu Xiuming, has committed a huge crime and thus was escorted back here to the capital.

159
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:43,750
Perhaps the "dragon" will be angered and he will lose his head. <br> <i>(T/N: dragon represents the emperor)</i>

160
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:47,260
Your little life is about to be taken away yet you're still here bluffing and blustering.

161
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:49,700
She thinks she flew up the branch and became a phoenix.

162
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:53,340
In the end, her true colors will show.

163
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:55,140
It seems that you have already forgotten what happened, Elder Sister Zi

164
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:58,570
Back then, if you didn't force me to get married, then perhaps the person who would die is you.

165
00:14:58,570 --> 00:15:00,390
- You—! <br> - Elder Sister Zi.

166
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:02,640
If she insists on staying here at the Rui Royal Manor,

167
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:07,580
then seeing that we are sisters, we could reluctantly agree to it.

168
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:12,670
It's just... with your aptitude, you can only be a maidservant who does some

169
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:14,480
brainless errands.

170
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:17,720
That's right. Lately, it's been quite busy here at the manor.

171
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:21,630
I think our front yard hasn't been cleaned yet.

172
00:15:21,630 --> 00:15:24,590
I wonder if Young Sister Jin... No!

173
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:29,500
...the general's lady has the time or not. <br> - You—

174
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:37,290
Since you want me to sweep the floor, then I'll just do it, Elder Sister Zi.

175
00:15:37,290 --> 00:15:39,550
Good. Hurry up.

176
00:15:39,550 --> 00:15:41,490
We're leaving.

177
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,780
These two people are such bullies.

178
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,450
Why should we listen to them?

179
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:53,570
They just want to boast in their temporary happiness, that's all. Don't mind them.

180
00:15:53,570 --> 00:15:55,650
"Once a tiger comes down from the mountain, it's bullied by dogs." <br> <i>(T/N: when someone loses their power/influence, his subordinates insult him)</i>

181
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:58,700
Once the general returns, we'll teach them a lesson!

182
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,840
Keep watch here. I'm going to see Mother first.

183
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,340
Okay.

184
00:16:02,910 --> 00:16:06,180
- Mother! <br> - Jin'er. <br> - Mother!

185
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,930
My Jin'er is back!

186
00:16:12,050 --> 00:16:14,380
Let me take a look at you.

187
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:16,500
I heard that beyond the city walls, there are many hardships. <br> <i>(T/N: literal translation "the wind blows and the rain hits")</i>

188
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:19,960
I think my Jin'er has gotten thinner.

189
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,830
The general dotes on me just like you, Mother.

190
00:16:21,830 --> 00:16:24,090
I am restricted in no way at the general's manor.

191
00:16:24,090 --> 00:16:28,040
Everyone at the manor treats me very well. I have been very well.

192
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:31,890
That's good then. Seeing you and the general so in love with each other,

193
00:16:31,890 --> 00:16:33,820
I am very happy.

194
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:38,130
My Jin'er finally doesn't have to suffer anymore.

195
00:16:38,130 --> 00:16:41,230
Mother, has Royal Father kept his promise?

196
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:43,950
Did anyone mistreat you while I was gone?

197
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:46,300
I am very well. I am very well.

198
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:48,850
You don't need to worry about me.

199
00:16:49,990 --> 00:16:51,500
Mother, there's no need to lie to me.

200
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:55,470
I just came in through the door and I saw Shen Zi and Sheng Jing those two brats moving things out from this room.

201
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:58,690
If Royal Father didn't keep his promise, I will ask for justice.

202
00:16:58,690 --> 00:17:02,070
I am doing very well. You really do not need to worry about me.

203
00:17:02,070 --> 00:17:04,760
But the general's situation,

204
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:06,590
what is going on?

205
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:10,040
Mother, I believe that the general will surely be fine.

206
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:14,040
He already went to go report back to the imperial court. He'll return very soon.

207
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:17,280
That's good then. That's good then.

208
00:17:18,330 --> 00:17:22,430
I have been here praying for blessings for you and the general every day.

209
00:17:22,430 --> 00:17:24,840
I hope you two can successfully get through these difficulties.

210
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:28,470
<i> - Has the courtyard been cleaned yet? <br> - What's the hurry?! </i>

211
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:32,080
Mother, wait for me for a moment.

212
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:34,020
I'll go for a bit and return.

213
00:17:38,850 --> 00:17:41,740
<i>The criminal officer, Chu Xiuming, made false reports about the soldiers</i>

214
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:43,910
<i>and embezzled from military funds.</i>

215
00:17:47,610 --> 00:17:49,790
The accounts of the Chu Family Army are right here.

216
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:52,080
The evidence is irrefutable!

217
00:17:58,230 --> 00:18:00,870
Your Majesty, the general strictly and impartially enforces military discipline.

218
00:18:00,870 --> 00:18:02,550
He treats soldiers as his brothers.

219
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:07,390
There is no way he would secretly take from the military funds.

220
00:18:10,250 --> 00:18:15,550
I know that you old subordinates of Chu Xiuming, who followed him into battles for many years,

221
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:17,980
won't believe this.

222
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:20,760
I also am not willing to believe it.

223
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:23,480
I have always cherished your great general.

224
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:25,300
I appreciated him very much

225
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:28,150
and promoted him in terms of official position as well as social status. I rewarded him with a manor.

226
00:18:28,150 --> 00:18:30,950
I have never mistreated you!

227
00:18:30,950 --> 00:18:34,240
Unfortunately, it's hard to fathom human nature.

228
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:37,990
Chu Xiuming. Your "heart of a tiger and wolf" has been exposed. <br> <i>(T/N: heart of greed and cruelty)</i>

229
00:18:37,990 --> 00:18:41,800
It makes me... feel great pain.

230
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:48,950
Your Majesty, every nation has its own laws and every household has its own rules.

